lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Sun sinkin' low, paintin' the sky gold
Windows down, cruise control, stories unfold
Mike behind the wheel, grippin' the leather
Allen in the passenger seat, laughin' like he never

(Chorus)
Packed a bowl, fire it up, let the smoke fly
Local Natives on the speakers, hummin' real high
Wind in our hair, asphalt unwindin'
Just another summer night, freedom we're findin'
